      • getAdditionalInfluence

        protected Float getAdditionalInfluence(GradoopId firstMasterDataId,
                                       String firstMasterDataMap,
                                       GradoopId secondMasterDataId,
                                       String secondMasterDataMap)
        Calculates additional relative influence for two master data objects. The addition is increased if the objects share the same location or the same holding. If not 1.0f is returned.
        Parameters:
        firstMasterDataId - gradoop id of the first master data object
        firstMasterDataMap - name of the map of the first master data object
        secondMasterDataId - gradoop id of the second master data object
        secondMasterDataMap - name of the map of the second master data object
        Returns:
        float value representing relative addition to the master data objects qualities
